## 5. High-Level Mapping Summary
- Mapping Type: **1:1 (Direct Column Mapping)**
- Transformation Required: **No (Direct Copy)**
- Primary Key: **EMPLOYEE_ID**
- Incremental Column (if applicable): **LAST_UPDATED_TS**

---

## 6. Detailed Column Mapping

| # | Source Column       | Source Data Type | Target Column        | Target Data Type | Nullable  | Key Type | Transformation Rule  | Remarks                          |
|---|---------------------|------------------|----------------------|------------------|-----------|----------|----------------------|----------------------------------|
| 1 | EMPLOYEE_ID         | INT              | EMPLOYEE_ID          | BIGINT           | NOT NULL  | PK       | Direct 1:1           | Primary Key                      |
| 2 | EMPLOYEE_NUMBER     | VARCHAR(50)      | EMPLOYEE_NUMBER      | STRING           | NULL      | NK       | Direct 1:1           | Business Employee Number         |
| 3 | FIRST_NAME          | VARCHAR(100)     | FIRST_NAME           | STRING           | NULL      | -        | Direct 1:1           |                                  |
| 4 | LAST_NAME           | VARCHAR(100)     | LAST_NAME            | STRING           | NULL      | -        | Direct 1:1           |                                  |
| 5 | EMAIL_ADDRESS       | VARCHAR(255)     | EMAIL_ADDRESS        | STRING           | NULL      | -        | Direct 1:1           |                                  |
| 6 | PHONE_NUMBER        | VARCHAR(50)      | PHONE_NUMBER         | STRING           | NULL      | -        | Direct 1:1           |                                  |
| 7 | DATE_OF_BIRTH       | DATE             | DATE_OF_BIRTH        | DATE             | NULL      | -        | Direct 1:1           |                                  |
| 8 | HIRE_DATE           | DATE             | HIRE_DATE            | DATE             | NULL      | -        | Direct 1:1           |                                  |
| 9 | TERMINATION_DATE    | DATE             | TERMINATION_DATE     | DATE             | NULL      | -        | Direct 1:1           |                                  |
| 10 | JOB_TITLE          | VARCHAR(150)     | JOB_TITLE            | STRING           | NULL      | -        | Direct 1:1           |                                  |
| 11 | DEPARTMENT_ID      | INT              | DEPARTMENT_ID        | BIGINT           | NULL      | FK       | Direct 1:1           | Foreign Key to Department        |
| 12 | MANAGER_ID         | INT              | MANAGER_ID           | BIGINT           | NULL      | FK       | Direct 1:1           | Self-Referencing FK              |
| 13 | EMPLOYMENT_STATUS  | VARCHAR(50)      | EMPLOYMENT_STATUS    | STRING           | NULL      | -        | Direct 1:1           | Active / Inactive / Terminated   |
| 14 | SALARY_AMOUNT      | DECIMAL(18,2)    | SALARY_AMOUNT        | NUMERIC(18,2)    | NULL      | -        | Direct 1:1           |                                  |
| 15 | CURRENCY_CODE      | CHAR(3)          | CURRENCY_CODE        | STRING           | NULL      | -        | Direct 1:1           | ISO Currency Code                |
| 16 | SRC_CREATE_TS      | TIMESTAMP        | SRC_CREATE_TS        | TIMESTAMP        | NULL      | -        | Direct 1:1           | Source Audit Column              |
| 17 | SRC_UPDATE_TS      | TIMESTAMP        | SRC_UPDATE_TS        | TIMESTAMP        | NULL      | -        | Direct 1:1           | Source Audit Column              |
| 18 | LOAD_TS            | N/A              | LOAD_TS              | TIMESTAMP        | NOT NULL  | -        | System Generated     | ETL Load Timestamp               |

---

## 7. Key Definitions
- **PK:** Primary Key
- **NK:** Natural Key
- **FK:** Foreign Key

---

## 8. Data Quality Rules

| Rule ID | Column Name        | Rule Description                                        | Severity |
|---------|--------------------|---------------------------------------------------------|----------|
| DQ-01   | EMPLOYEE_ID        | Must not be NULL                                        | Critical |
| DQ-02   | EMAIL_ADDRESS      | Must follow valid email format                          | High     |
| DQ-03   | HIRE_DATE          | Must be less than or equal to current date              | Medium   |
| DQ-04   | EMPLOYMENT_STATUS  | Must be one of (Active, Inactive, Terminated)           | High     |

---

## 9. Load & Reconciliation Checks
- **Record Count:** Source count must match Target count
- **Primary Key Uniqueness:** No duplicate EMPLOYEE_ID in Target
- **Null Check:** No NULLs in mandatory columns
- **Incremental Check:** Only changed records loaded based on UPDATE_TS

---

## 10. Assumptions & Notes
- All fields are mapped using direct one-to-one mapping.
- No business transformations are applied.
- Target audit column **LOAD_TS** is system-generated.
- Any future schema changes must be reflected in this document.

